text = "\"Listen, kid. I'm getting old. I won't always be around... And if someone calls, we need eyes on this room\", Grandpa told me.

\"So please, promise me you'll never take your eyes off that screen. Not until the day you die. No chance in hell we're the last humans in this god-forsaken galaxy.\""

[node name="RunningTextPart2" parent="RunningTextBox" index="4" instance=ExtResource( 5 )]
text = "I'd been floating through space for what feels like ages with nothing to do. Being a galaxy guardian was lame.
      	  
But then it happened. I got a distress signal from a ship.
"

