SOS!
– TRANSMISSION END –"

[node name="RunningTextPart6" parent="RunningTextBox" index="6" instance=ExtResource( 5 )]
text = "\"SS Monolith? I know that one! That's the ship my friend is on!\"

Quickly I set off and enabled my hyperdrive."

[node name="RunningTextPart4" parent="RunningTextBox" index="7" instance=ExtResource( 5 )]
text = "Upon arriving I was met with utter destruction and chaos.

Some alien lifeforms seemed to have ransacked the ship, leaving nobody alive.

Nobody? I heard distant noises from a storage module."

[node name="RunningTextPart5" parent="RunningTextBox" index="8" instance=ExtResource( 5 )]
